OL,3,GOPINIONCOfcom decision regarding STV News
OL,4,Ccould set precedent for other ITV
OL,5,Cregions
OL,6,
OL,7,FOfcom's decision on STV's proposal to
OL,8,Fstop providing a distinct news service
OL,9,Ffor the north of Scotland could set a
OL,10,Fprecedent.
OL,12,FIf the STV North service goes, it would
OL,13,Fbe hard to refuse any requests for
OL,14,Fsimilar changes to English regions.
OL,16,FSTV's plan is to produce a single news
OL,17,Fprogramme for both Central and Northern
OL,18,FScotland.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
