OL,4,Ccould set precedent for other ITV
OL,5,Cregions
OL,6,
OL,7,FOfcom will need to approve the plan -
OL,8,Fit could potentially block it or secure
OL,9,Fmodifications.
OL,11,FDetails of the consultation process
OL,12,Fhave still to be announced.
OL,14,FBut imagine this.
OL,16,FIf STV gets approval for this, how
OL,17,Fmight ITV feel about some of its
OL,18,Fregional commitments?
