OL,3,GOPINIONCOfcom decision regarding STV News
OL,4,Ccould set precedent for other ITV
OL,5,Cregions
OL,6,
OL,7,FWe all know the pressure commercial
OL,8,Fbroadcasters are under with cuts to the
OL,9,Fsoaps and daytime due to kick in within
OL,10,F3 months.
OL,12,FSo, imagine if ITV started to think
OL,13,Fabout its English regions again in a
OL,14,Fyear or two?
OL,16,FCould a joint programme for West and
OL,17,FWestcountry be on the cards? Or the end
OL,18,Fof some splits.
