OL,3,GOPINIONCOfcom decision regarding STV News
OL,4,Ccould set precedent for other ITV
OL,5,Cregions
OL,6,
OL,7,FOf course, it would mean a poorer local
OL,8,Fservice but if a service is not
OL,9,Ffinancially viable can it still be
OL,10,Fsubsidised?
OL,12,FHow would Ofcom respond? It would be
OL,13,Fhard to say that Westcountry's current
OL,14,Fprovision had to be maintained after
OL,15,Fditching Grampian.
OL,17,FCould a proposal to replace Channel
OL,18,Fwith a recorded sub-opt from
OL,19,FSouthampton prove acceptable?
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
