OL,3,GOPINIONCOfcom decision regarding STV News
OL,4,Ccould set precedent for other ITV
OL,5,Cregions
OL,6,
OL,7,FAnd what about the level of regional
OL,8,Foutput required in Wales and Northern
OL,9,FIreland?
OL,11,FThere is no suggestion at present of
OL,12,Fimminent cuts but the point remains -
OL,13,Fadvertising is down and every
OL,14,Fcross-subsidy will have to be
OL,15,Fconsidered sooner or later.
OL,17,FOnce a decision is taken to effectively
OL,18,Fscrap an official channel 3 region -
OL,19,Fi.e., Grampian - how can a request to
OL,20,Fscrap another be flatly rejected? And
OL,21,Fsub-regions are especially vulnerable.
